<section class="section section-dark">
    <h1>Contributing</h1>
    <p class="paragraph-intro">
        Whether you are new to Ember or you have been using it for years,
        we'd love to have your help.
        Ember is an Open Source project that relies on volunteer time
        and donations.
    </p>
</section>

<section>
    <h2>Make your first PR</h2>
    <p>Visit
        <a href="https://help-wanted.emberjs.com/">Ember Help Wanted</a>
        to see a collection of issues that need volunteers.
        Look for those marked "good first issue."
        If you need help finding something to work on,
        making your first PR, or you have questions,
        post in the #dev-ember-learning channel on
        <LinkTo @route="community">Ember Community Discord</LinkTo>.
    </p>
</section>

